to weave a tight social fabric,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1147000' id='t-1147000'>this feeling of urgent optimism
and the desire for epic meaning.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
19:22
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1151000' id='t-1151000'>I really hope that we can come together
to play games that matter,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1154533' id='t-1154533'>to survive on this planet
for another century.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1156783' id='t-1156783'>That's my hope, that you will join me
in making and playing games like this.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1160459' id='t-1160459'>When I look forward to the next decade,
I know two things for sure:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1164283' id='t-1164283'>that we can make
any future we can imagine,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1167000' id='t-1167000'>and we can play any games
we want, so I say:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1170134' id='t-1170134'>Let the world-changing games begin.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
